The BigDFT project was an European project (FP6-NEST) from 2005 to 2008.

Four institutions were implicated in the BigDFT project (version < 1.1):
- Commissariat a l'Energie Atomique (T. Deutsch),
- University of Basel (S. Goedecker)
- Université catholique de Louvain (X. Gonze)
- Christian-Albrechts Universität zu Kiel (R. Schneider)

From 2010, three laboratories are contributing: L_Sim (CEA), UNIBAS and ESRF.


